reviews.review_text: The Best Version Thank you for preserving a flawless version of this beautiful show. The Other One will make your bowels fall out of your pants.
The good ole Grateful Dead 3 of some of the best nights of my youth
niiice Awesome sound on this recording, very good show in the middle of a terrific three night run at the "local skating rink." Hiiiilights for me are Here Comes Sunshine and Eyes>OMSN.
